Error 113  stands for "No route to host".  It looks like the problem is caused by the preceeding 0s in the ip address of the share name. This for some reason gets treated as a hostname instead of an ip address. Please modify the fstab line to 

//192.168.1.11/hcmeyer	/home/hcmeyer/Samba	cifs	noauto,users	0 0

and let me know if this fixes the issue.
